pm install serverless-localstack

desplegar
serverless deploy --stage local

listar los buckets
aws --endpoint-url=http://localhost:4566 s3 ls 

crear un bucket llamado my-serverless-bucket
aws --endpoint-url=http://localhost:4566 s3 mb s3://my-serverless-bucket

configurando url mas amigables
npm install serverless-offline --save-dev